Title: Relates to the effectiveness of the New York black car operators' injury compensation fund, inc.
Summary: Extends the effectiveness of the New York black car operators' injury compensation fund, inc., for an additional three years.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend chapter 730 of the laws of 2019, amending the executive law relating to the authority of the New York black car operators' injury compensation fund, inc., in relation to the effectiveness thereof
